  <outcomes>
    <primaryOutcome>
      <outcome>Ability to reverse anticoagulant effect in vitro of dabigatran or rivarovaban - The ability of nonspecific coagulation factors to reverse anticoagulant effect in vitro as measured by dilute thrombin time, Calibrated automated thrombinoscope, thromboelastogram and Rotem</outcome>
      <timepoint>Two hours after ingestion of anticoagulant dose</timepoint>
    </primaryOutcome>
  </outcomes>
