  <ethicsAndSummary>
    <summary>New anticoagulants are being introduced to replace warfarin. These drugs do not require
      monitoring and are safer. There is currently no recommended way to reverse these drugs
      rapidly in the event of undue bleeding or need for emergency surgery. This is a lab study to
      look at ways to reverse the drugs rapidly</summary>
